00:41:18.240 --> 00:41:19.540
&gt;&gt; Tillie Walden: Oh.

00:41:19.540 --> 00:41:20.840
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: And they
both got to wear masks.

00:41:20.840 --> 00:41:22.140
She was just--

00:41:22.140 --> 00:41:23.440
&gt;&gt; Penelope Bagieu: Yeah,
and she's the only woman.

00:41:23.440 --> 00:41:24.740
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Wow.

00:41:24.740 --> 00:41:26.040
&gt;&gt; Penelope Bagieu: So, yeah,
so, and for a long time,

00:41:26.040 --> 00:41:29.300
I was really, even just to see
her face was too much for me.

00:41:29.300 --> 00:41:33.420
And then, one day, I heard that
she was actually a schoolteacher

00:41:33.420 --> 00:41:36.060
to begin with and that she
loved children, and I thought,

00:41:36.060 --> 00:41:38.840
what a curse it must've been
for her because for the rest

00:41:38.840 --> 00:41:41.980
of her life, she was, I think
probably kids were running away

00:41:41.980 --> 00:41:43.510
screaming whenever they saw her.

00:41:43.510 --> 00:41:46.840
And then, I heard that she had
been a single mom struggling

00:41:46.840 --> 00:41:50.120
to get parts, and she wanted
to play romantic roles,

00:41:50.120 --> 00:41:54.530
but all the casting directors
told her she was too ugly

00:41:54.530 --> 00:41:55.900
to play that.

00:41:55.900 --> 00:41:58.710
And so she thought, okay,
then plan B, I'm going to be,

00:41:58.710 --> 00:42:01.200
if I can't be the pretty one,
I'm going to be the scary one

00:42:01.200 --> 00:42:03.160
because I'm really
good at being scary.

00:42:03.160 --> 00:42:07.660
And so she heard that they were
auditioning the part of a witch

00:42:07.660 --> 00:42:10.350
in a movie, and so
she went there,

00:42:10.350 --> 00:42:16.540
and she became the most
famous witch in the world, so.

00:42:16.540 --> 00:42:17.840
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Yeah.

00:42:17.840 --> 00:42:19.140
&gt;&gt; Tillie Walden: Wow.

00:42:19.140 --> 00:42:20.440
&gt;&gt; Penelope Bagieu: Yeah.

00:42:20.440 --> 00:42:21.740
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna:
And so I just want

00:42:21.740 --> 00:42:23.040
